snippet.textDisplay: The bengal region has a vast array of musical genres. It had existed in this region for thousands of years. Ever since the partition in 1947 two seperate nations emerged but the delicate musical taste of its indigenous people remained unchanged. Artists like Ayub Bacchu, Sayan Chowdhury,  James, Anupam Roy, Mizan made the vast collection even more rich during the following years. Through this hopefully the world will come to know about the vastness of bengali music. Will love to see covers from James, Tuhin, Anupam Roy, Arnob and Mizan.
